column5: Heading to Temagami for a Houseboat wkd and looking to hook up with some walleye. Has anybody fished this lake in early summer? Is there a particular area of the lake that produces? I'll be trolling out of a 14' with electronics looking for humps etc. Any tips appreciated. Would also love to get into some lakers, but haven't done it before.
Good Luck at Temagami, I will be at Red Cedar Lake just south of you for the week. Have heard no reports on either lake yet.
